{"tid":2436640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多國擬推疫苗護照 世衞反對籲勿鬆懈  指「接種者仍可能播毒」","createTime":"2021-03-07T09:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T20:35:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"28115c082851663f79f4ece1af1a1ea63b55b413","tid":2436640,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210307/ZRET4XXCSBBD7HXOZEI7NFCKMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210307%2FZRET4XXCSBBD7HXOZEI7NFCKMI%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=509c4585\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210307%2FZRET4XXCSBBD7HXOZEI7NFCKMI%2F&h=dc7c0cbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210307/ZRET4XXCSBBD7HXOZEI7NFCKMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n多國擬推疫苗護照 世衞反對籲勿鬆懈 <br />\n指「接種者仍可能播毒」<br />\n<br />\n【意見不一】被武漢肺炎疫情「囚禁」一年後，人人都渴望重享自由，隨着疫苗面世，多國有意實行「疫苗護照」制度讓社會恢復正常運作，歐盟上周亦公佈正籌備設立接種疫苗證明的機制，但世界衞生組織（WHO）專家表明對構思有疑慮，因為疫苗效力可持續多久仍不確定，而且接種疫苗後不代表不會把病毒傳播給其他人，接種疫苗不該被視為「病毒不侵」的通行證。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：注射後欠指引 美民眾疑慮日增<br />\n<br />\n世衞歐洲地區辦事處主任克盧格在德國《世界報》前日刊登的訪問中指出，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0NtDcdihhz1QJsF0gwB6PEWdkm0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LI3B55QE6RFPRHKGRS347SQQQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0NtDcdihhz1QJsF0gwB6PEWdkm0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLI3B55QE6RFPRHKGRS347SQQQ4.jpg&h=6413712d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■疫苗護照被視為民眾重獲自由的希望，但世衞對計劃有保留。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冰島以色列率先實施<br />\n<br />\n其實不少國家已實行這類通行證制度。冰島上月底已開始向完成接種的公民發出數碼通行證，而持有接種證明的外國人亦毋須於入境後進行隔離。巴林和以色列都設有智能手機程式，讓完成接種的公民下載，通行證列出了姓名、出生日期及接種的疫苗品牌等資料。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟受到依賴觀光業的成員國壓力，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W-P7rmqmVeX7_G8D5UAtrgYcwkw=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O7G2XK4EJFDZLFVABVYQYUJKSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW-P7rmqmVeX7_G8D5UAtrgYcwkw%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO7G2XK4EJFDZLFVABVYQYUJKSQ.jpg&h=ad2fecaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■武肺仍然肆虐，只有少數國家允許一般民眾出入境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「會浪費疫苗帶來的曙光」<br />\n<br />\n公共衞生專家非常擔心疫苗面世成為各國放鬆警惕的契機，最近多國的新一波疫情正是警號。世衞緊急項目負責人瑞安前日在網上簡佈會提醒，別「以為已捱過疫情；疫情還未結束。若我們掉以輕心，各國會再爆第三波、第四波疫情」。<br />\n<br />\n傳染力更強的巴西變種病毒肆虐下，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n克盧格亦指出，要是變種病毒廣泛傳播，而接種工作推動緩慢，「病毒又會重佔上風」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xe0ngxeTXexYz_4ETR7yCun_Cpo=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CJ4UKMVHWVD4JL47XMNMYS7CVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fxe0ngxeTXexYz_4ETR7yCun_Cpo%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCJ4UKMVHWVD4JL47XMNMYS7CVY.jpg&h=8fae6749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多國因武肺封關，限制了大部份民眾外遊。路透社"},{"pid":"a60504314f2bbc23f3c751470dcb70dcece90f03","tid":2436640,"uid":31773,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"睇黎世衛都差唔多"},{"pid":"11955717b55bacb42499e0140cd7463d3c85294f","tid":2436640,"uid":290372,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"咁打黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306a45c22cc2a2d3df84efad26c611ee79c30c98","tid":2436640,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"廣泛傳開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /